devdoc.details: Contract for managing a single election

addCandidate(uint256,uint256).details: Add a candidate to a position

params._candidateId: ID of the candidate to add
params._positionId: ID of the position the candidate is running for

constructor.details: Constructor to create a new election

params._endTime: End time of the election as Unix timestamp
params._positionIds: Array of position IDs to include in the election
params._startTime: Start time of the election as Unix timestamp

getCandidateCount(uint256).details: Get the candidate count for a specific position

returns._0: The number of candidates for the position

getCandidateVotes(uint256,uint256).details: Get the vote count for a specific candidate in a position

returns._0: The number of votes received by the candidate

getCandidatesForPosition(uint256).details: Get all candidates for a specific position

returns._0: Array of candidate IDs for the position

getPositionCandidate(uint256,uint256).details: Get a candidate ID for a position by index

params._index: Index of the candidate in the position's candidate array

returns._0: The ID of the candidate at the specified index

getPositionCount().details: Get the number of positions in the election

getWinner(uint256).details: Get the winner for a specific position

params._positionId: ID of the position to check

returns._0: The ID of the winning candidate (or 0 if no votes)

hasVoted(address,uint256).details: Check if a voter has voted for a specific position

params._positionId: ID of the position to check
params._voter: Address of the voter to check

returns._0: True if the voter has voted for the position

isCandidateInPosition(uint256,uint256).details: Check if a candidate is running for a specific position

params._candidateId: ID of the candidate to check
params._positionId: ID of the position to check

returns._0: True if the candidate is running for the position

isValidPosition(uint256).details: Check if a position ID is valid for this election

params._positionId: ID of the position to check

returns._0: True if the position ID is valid

setElectionPhase(uint8).details: Change the phase of the election

vote(uint256,uint256).details: Cast a vote for a candidate in a position

params._candidateId: ID of the candidate to vote for
params._positionId: ID of the position to vote for

whitelistVoter(address).details: Whitelist a voter to participate in the election

params._voter: Address of the voter to whitelist

params._voters: Array of voter addresses to whitelist
